            <h3>What this Privacy Policy Covers?</h3>
            <p> This Privacy Policy covers Uvah Care's treatment of your Personally Identifiable Information and Sensitive Personal Data or Information that Uvah Care collects when you use any of the Services offered by Uvah Care that are listed on our Website and/or Apps
