            Uvah Care also automatically receives and records information on Uvah Care's server logs from your browser including your IP address, Uvah Care's Cookie information and the webpage you have requested to view.
            Uvah Care uses your Personally Identifiable Information to fulfil your requests for Services that you require and other offers of Uvah Care, and to contact you about any special offers and new services that Uvah Care offers, or may list on its Website at any time in the future.
            Uvah Care may also use your Personally Identifiable Information and Sensitive Personal Data or Information for internal purposes, such as auditing, data analysis and research to improve the offerings of Service on our Website and customer communications.
